wdi2-TX.VAL.MMTL.ZS.UN.def: Ores and metals comprise the commodities in SITC sections 27 (crude fertilizer, minerals nes); 28 (metalliferous ores, scrap); and 68 (non-ferrous metals).
wdi2-TX.VAL.MMTL.ZS.UN.name: Ores and metals exports
wdi2-TX.VAL.MMTL.ZS.UN.source: World Bank staff estimates through the WITS platform from the Comtrade database maintained by the United Nations Statistics Division.
